<subSubSection id="D9BA65676B39FFE5FF52AAD7BE3813C8" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="911F36EC6B39FFE5FF52AAD7BE3813C8" blockId="16.[151,1436,1301,1927]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
<emphasis id="A3D4EAFE6B39FFE5FF52AAD7BE441340" bold="true" box="[197,321,1781,1807]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Remarks:</emphasis>
This species is being known as Jarad-al-ushr which means 
<taxonomicName id="56A04D6F6B39FFE5FB81AAD7BBFD1341" box="[1046,1272,1781,1806]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Apocynaceae" genus="Calotropis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Gentianales" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="procera">
